ng the brand’s flagship K series. The device features a “Flowing Gold White” finish, large rounded corners, ultra-narrow bezels, and a unibody metal “volcanic” camera housing. Next to the camera sits a large speaker labeled “Sound by Bose,” marking [&#8230;]]]></description>
